th a merry group of monsters, but he is bored stiff! One night, he secretly sneaks out of the manor along with his trusted bulldog, Phantomato, on a quest to find some new friends.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":0.3631,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/mLd9FVJTwnPO3ERv82ea5IZo6Hl.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/dAWrub4aTNMsh0pnYBiGPKZiREr.jpg","original_title":"Petit Vampire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":589973,"adult":false,"title":"SamSam","video":false,"overview":"SamSam, the smallest of the great heroes, has still not discovered his first superpower, while at home and at school, everyone has one! Faced with the worry of his parents and the mockery of his comrades, he goes in search of this hidden power. With the help of Mega, the new mysterious student of his school, Samsam embarks on this adventure full of cosmic monsters ...","genre_ids":[16,10751,878,12,35],"popularity":0.3545,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/nNMAglUfOuDuyAKYSmXzFkBeNha.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/5T2kiBvi169qnCY8ul3btCRfJuf.jpg","original_title":"SamSam","original_language":"fr"},{"id":418956,"adult":false,"title":"The Ugly Duckling","video":false,"overview":"An outcast duckling's search for a family to accept him leads to constant rejection before learning his true identity as a swan.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.9617,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/nCkMoq2penMxvdhQa0LGwK1G6fJ.jpg","release_date":"1939-04-07","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/woMB1t6cBbS9xPzZzsv8DI7IOxV.jpg","original_title":"The Ugly Duckling","original_language":"en"},{"id":763577,"adult":false,"title":"Spiritpact","video":false,"overview":"Yang Jinghua, a young heir to a family of exorcists, is left struggling alone after his parents’ deaths. Barely surviving, he encounters the wealthy and skilled exorcist Duanmu Xi while trying to fend off a spirit. After a fatal accident, Yang awakens to find himself in a contract with Dua