l_title":"올드보이","original_language":"ko"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.5713,"vote_count":20531,"poster_path":"/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-08","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":679,"adult":false,"title":"Aliens","video":false,"overview":"Ripley, the sole survivor of the Nostromo's deadly encounter with the monstrous Alien, returns to Earth after drifting through space in hypersleep for 57 years. Although her story is initially met with skepticism, she agrees to accompany a team of Colonial Marines back to LV-426.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":12.7427,"vote_count":10609,"poster_path":"/r1x5JGpyqZU8PYhbs4UcrO1Xb6x.jpg","release_date":"1986-07-18","vote_average":7.956,"backdrop_path":"/4kix6fAblJIH6eMs0Ku2loyZJXK.jpg","original_title":"Aliens","original_language":"en"},{"id":754,"adult":false,"title":"Face/Off","video":false,"overview":"In order to foil a terrorist plot, an FBI agent undergoes facial transplant surgery and assumes the identity of a criminal mastermind. The plan turns sour when the criminal wakes up prematurely and seeks revenge.","genre_ids":[28,80,878],"popularity":6.5992,"vote_count":5766,"poster_path":"/69Xzn8UdPbVnmqSChKz2RTpoNfB.jpg","release_date":"1997-06-27","vote_average":7.052,"backdrop_path":"/tsSWHgaFlzzkp3o976juBZbmcs2.jpg","original_title":"Face/Off","original_language":"en"},{"id":765,"adult":false,"title":"Evil Dead II","video":false,"overview":"Ash Williams and his girlfriend Linda find a log cabin in the woods with a voice recording from an archeologist who had recorded himself reciting ancient chants from \"The Book of the Dead.\" As they play the recording an evil power is unleashed taking over Linda's body.","genre_ids":[27,35,14],"popularity":3.8434,"vote_count":3397,"poster_path":"/4zqCKJVHUolGs6C5AZwAZqLWixW.jpg","release_date":"1987-03-13","vote_average":7.545,"backdrop_path":"/dOvEJK2u0slAGTfhdZOjnNgCQet.jpg","original_title":"Evil Dead II","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":13.7456,"vote_count":20501,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":421594,"adult":false,"title":"Nana and Kaoru","video":false,"overview":"Kaoru is a 17-year-old boy with an SM fetish, secretly dreaming of an SM relationship with his childhood friend Nana. One day Kaoru's mother asks Nana to hide all his SM toys so that he will study for a change. However, Nana finds the leather one-piece that Kaoru bought and tries it on, but she accidentally locks it and does not have the key! This is the beginning of a very strange relationship...","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.7443,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qCWi9MHrRctaCR82Rw3SZH20P2i.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-29","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/u7rRtrJqngEFmptLsXQayC2cP4r.jpg","original_title":"ナナとカオル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":766423,"adult":false,"title":"Puparia","video":false,"overview":"Something is about to change drastically, and the only thing to do is to witness it.","genre_ids":[16,18,14],"popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/3KRpbwNDrQ8cqKoVknoPqqtrpAO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-23","vote_average":7.958,"backdrop_path":"/6HRvFDiP894qvRLMu0nM0WeNbiC.jpg","original_title":"Puparia","original_language":"ja"},{"id":766507,"adult":false,"title":"Prey","video":false,"overview":"When danger threatens her camp, the fierce and highly skilled Comanche warrior Naru sets out to protect her people. But the prey she stalks turns out to be a highly evolved alien predator with a technically advanced arsenal.","genre_ids":[53,28,878],"popularity":12.1264,"vote_count":7516,"poster_path":"/2FKjLRt7oK1bRRIrxgWmthbBdFh.jpg","release_date":"2022-08-02","vote_average":7.667,"backdrop_path":"/sNhzcUw5cg4JwICjnHZ5XhTKNrU.jpg","original_title":"Prey","original_language":"en"},{"id":949394,"adult":false,"title":"Ensemble Stars!! -Road to Show--","video":false,"overview":"Ensemble Square - a brand new building in the middle of the city where countless people come and go. It’s home to four offices belonging to idols who spend their days singing and dancing. Films starring the Ensemble Square idols have been nominated for the Idol Film Festival (IFF), an annual festival held in New York City, and representative idols are selected to attend. The boys jet off to NYC to attend the festival and reception party, and afterward, head out on the town to see the sights and sounds. But a suspicious shadow is creeping up on them…","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7096,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/hW4Y4Fy8khf4D3tlvwV82txg1uy.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eTfbiJANxSTnrISIL9JSGeI8uur.jpg","original_title":"あんさんぶるスターズ！！-Road to Show!!-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":919,"adult":false,"title":"Blood: The Last Vampire","video":false,"overview":"In Japan, the vampire-hunter Saya, who is a powerful original, is sent by her liaison with the government, David, posed as a teenage student to the Yokota High School on the eve of Halloween to hunt down vampires. Saya asks David to give a new katana to her. Soon she saves the school nurse Makiho Amano from two vampires disguised of classmates and Makiho witnesses her fight against the powerful demon.","genre_ids":[16,14,27],"popularity":1.1511,"vote_count":362,"poster_path":"/uRwR5lcl55n5JSaTiYPwp5KjP6A.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/17s9ojb8j8QnBGCfqDUJraXLlFi.jpg","original_title":"BLOOD THE LAST VAMPIRE","original_language":"ja"},{"id":929,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla","video":false,"overview":"French nuclear tests irradiate an iguana into a giant monster that viciously attacks freighter ships in the Pacific Ocean. A team of experts, including Niko Tatopoulos, conclude that the oversized reptile is the culprit. Before long, the giant lizard is loose in Manhattan as the US military races to destroy the monster before it reproduces and it's spawn takes over the world.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"popularity":5.4875,"vote_count":4144,"poster_path":"/xJVl1I95StraYAwaNbBkVoWE2qA.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-20","vote_average":5.65,"backdrop_path":"/gT4XVSEmGKOJ0EgSEUTfCeqgEtc.jpg","original_title":"Godzilla","original_language":"en"},{"id":1293708,"adult":false,"title":"AIKa: Special Trial","video":false,"overview":"An OVA released between episodes 5 and 6 of AIKa, that takes place between episodes 4 and 5.","genre_ids":[16,878,35],"popularity":0.2816,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vLGtkrfmRqFh536eGmPpOUaLJiJ.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"origi